verbose_text: In this research, miR-370-3p was predicted to be a target of NEAT1 by starBase (XREF_FIG A) and the dual-luciferase reporter assay indicated that miR-370-3p markedly reduced the luciferase activity of WT-NEAT1 in LPS induced RAW 264.7 and HL-1 cells, rather than MUT-NEAT1 (XREF_FIG B, C).
evidence: miR-370-3p markedly reduced the luciferase activity of WT-NEAT1 in LPS-induced RAW 264.7 and HL-1 cells, rather than MUT-NEAT1
